{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Handcrafted by a Ukrainian solo developer:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/ihas_banner.png?t=1732201104\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wake up aboard a giant spaceship in this Sci-Fi Action-Puzzle FPS. With no recollection of your past, you are guided by a familiar voice claiming to be your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the Ship</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Swarming with hostile robots, you must make your way through the vessel, looking for an escape. As you navigate through energy gateways and shifting corridors, a lingering sense of foreboding tells you that secrets lie not far beneath the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/Portal.gif?t=1732201104\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Enhance and evolve your mechanical body</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your mission unfolds: As you venture through the ship, conquer the challenges that you face, and unearth your route to freedom, you find that you need to harness the potential of cybernetic enhancement. Seek out upgrade chips and learn to utilise them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/Pick_Up.gif?t=1732201104\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mod your weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you rove deeper, you realise that your enemies grow stronger. Equip your weapon with different mods to unlock its full potential. From a powerful laser beam to a hefty shotgun, customise your weapon to match your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/Mods.gif?t=1732201104\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Level editor (BETA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can\u2019t get enough after finishing the game? Don\u2019t worry \u2014 there\u2019s more, thanks to the community. Create and share your own levels through the Steam Workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/Level_Editor.gif?t=1732201104\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A captivating sci-fi adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Hours of tense FPS action, puzzles, and boss fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Explore the stunning environments of the spaceship IHAS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Navigate a seamless menu that won\u2019t break your immersion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Upgrade your weapon and mechanical body to adapt to the challenges ahead</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- (BETA) Connect with the community through the level editor, build, share and play brand new levels every day!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Assembly instructions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2187730/5e341786e53e5b11ff8a581cc53b12ebf922be13.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome on board","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2187730/e19fd5990c8ab5fb1fca0edb1efdd3a00551ec7a.jpg"},{"name":"The Lost Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2187730/89e2000a14ed4dce8690afdf463abc1499e2bb84.jpg"},{"name":"Unknown intentions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2187730/3a7f33cdb5c